          "descriptionFromReview": "I absolutely love living in this city. It's very clean, safe and things generally always work! This is something I miss when I travel to other cities in Europe and rest of the world. Also co-working spaces are growing tons. Though night life might be pretty \"boring\", it truly is what you make it. Get to know other expats and friends through meetups or friend of a friend, and you'll have an awesome time here!",
