          "population": "634161",
          "descriptionFromReview": "Jeju now has more coworking spaces across the island due to the remote worker trend going on in Korea. You would have to locate many via google maps though. 1 month stays are trending on the island as well for Korean remote workers. The free coworking space in Jeju city still exists.  New hotels are popping up as well.  Pandemic travel to the island has given it more life from mainland Koreans. It's good to see the new growth and tech efforts.  Jeju still has a lot more potential for the future. It's still a good value for a modern island lifestyle.",
