          "population": 64277.5,
          "descriptionFromReview": "I lived in Bowling Green for many years and found the people to be very friendly.  There is quite a variety of restaurants and some bars have live music.  The university offers many cultural activities, and Bowling Green's proximity to Nashville is good for the nightlife scene.  I found it very easy to make friends here.  On the downside, it gets extremely humid in summers and cool breezes are hard to come by.  Bowling Green has become very popular, so traffic has worsened over the past several years. ",
